        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/96/1",
        "text": [
          " : «اَلْمُطَلَّقَةُ تَحُجُّ فِي عِدَّتِهَا »."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.2913 - Al-'Ala' narrated from Muhammad ibn Muslim, from one of the Imams (as), who said:\n\"A divorced woman may perform Hajj during her waiting period ('iddah).\""
          ]
        }
      },
